process.name: Process Instance Summary Data by Application

processVariable.name: InstanceSummary
instancesStatuses
dataSeriesP

TWComponent.script: tw.local.sqlStatement select distinct application, name, value from ( SELECT lp1."NAME" application, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES."NAME" as name, count(LBI1.BPD_INSTANCE_ID) as value from LSW_BPD_INSTANCE LBI1, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES, lsw_project lp1 where LBI1.EXECUTION_STATUS(+) = LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES.STATUS_ID and lp1.PROJECT_ID = LBI1.PROJECT_ID(+) and lp1.IS_TOOLKIT = 'F' and lp1.IS_SYSTEM = 'F' and 0 < (select count(lbw3.BPD_INSTANCE_ID) from lsw_bpd_instance lbw3, LSW_PROJECT lp3, LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES lbsc3 where lbw3.EXECUTION_STATUS(+) = lbsc3.STATUS_ID and lp3.PROJECT_ID = lbw3.PROJECT_ID(+) and lp3.PROJECT_ID = lp1.PROJECT_ID and lbsc3.STATUS_ID in ('1','2','3','4','5','6')) group by lp1."NAME", LSW_BPD_STATUS_CODES."NAME" ) where value is not null order by name, application
